      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="fb52cb7a-bbb6-41ba-acd8-7c880f61fc45" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Sắc đẹp; vẻ đẹp</Vi>
          <En>The quality of being pleasing to the eye or mind, especially through harmony of form, color, or proportion.</En>
          <Example>She was struck by the beauty of the sunset over the ocean.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="ab0c2bc4-3b78-4750-b940-92d1f6a0192c">
              <Vi>Mô tả cảnh vật, con người, hoặc tác phẩm nghệ thuật gây ấn tượng mạnh về mặt thị giác hoặc cảm xúc.</Vi>
              <En>Used to describe a person, object, or scene that evokes admiration for its visual or aesthetic appeal.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="eda1b272-7cd8-4918-b773-9beffd5b910e">
              <Vi>Chỉ phẩm chất nội tại như lòng tốt, sự chân thành, tạo nên sức hút sâu sắc.</Vi>
              <En>Can refer to inner qualities such as kindness or authenticity that create deep personal appeal.</En>
